Want to build your own robots, turn your ideas into prototypes, control devices
with a computer, or make your own cell phone applications? It's a snap with
this book and the Arduino open source electronic prototyping platform. Get
started with six fun projects and achieve impressive results quickly.

Gain the know-how and experience to invent your own cool gadgets.

With Arduino, building your own embedded gadgets is easy, even for beginners.
Embedded systems are everywhere-inside cars, children's toys, and mobile
phones. This book will teach you the basics of embedded systems and help you
build your first gadget in just a few days. Each learn-as-you-build project
that follows will add to your knowledge and skills.
